{"tid":2285988,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"地火明夷的香港 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-11-14T14:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T14:46:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"104d031713da112ca194f1c38196c47650054bc8","tid":2285988,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201114/LJBHCVWNYBBZ7FEIKDKN7YUPS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201114%2FLJBHCVWNYBBZ7FEIKDKN7YUPS4%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1LdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=d6cb8ee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201114%2FLJBHCVWNYBBZ7FEIKDKN7YUPS4%2F&h=93daba7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201114/LJBHCVWNYBBZ7FEIKDKN7YUPS4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n地火明夷的香港 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x0_b6DZZCc9xFqbw8guUFudZANY=/500x260/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BYJPMQCRTZDP7P2YB7NLMZVFAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx0_b6DZZCc9xFqbw8guUFudZANY%3D%2F500x260%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBYJPMQCRTZDP7P2YB7NLMZVFAY.png&h=a9376b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前晚在飯局認識一位新朋友，他提起我寫的一篇專欄（2019年8月27日〈2020年的香港〉），文中說今年香港值「地火明夷」卦，光明隱淪於地，「百年制度，一日崩毀」，港人走的走，傷的傷，掌權者將自甘墮落，如今都一一應驗。<br />\n<br />\n近日四名立法會議員被人大常委DQ，無需走所謂香港司法程序，到了這個地步，《基本法》已經連遮羞布的作用都沒有了，只淪為荷蘭叻罩着自己那條小蟲的透明圍裙。學《成報》社論話齋，不如解散立法會，把議員薪水換成午餐肉派給市民更好&mdash;&mdash;當然只限「愛國」藍絲領取。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n。"}]}